{"tha-ap367:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap367:0.2":"Mandaravapupphiyavagga ","tha-ap367:0.3":"Ankolapupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap367:1.1":"“Padumo nama sambuddho, ","tha-ap367:1.2":"cittakute vasi tada; ","tha-ap367:1.3":"Disvana tam aham buddham, ","tha-ap367:1.4":"sayambhum aparajitam. ","tha-ap367:2.1":"Ankolam pupphitam disva, ","tha-ap367:2.2":"ocinitvanaham tada; ","tha-ap367:2.3":"Upagantvana sambuddham, ","tha-ap367:2.4":"pujayim padumam jinam. ","tha-ap367:3.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap367:3.2":"yam pupphamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap367:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap367:3.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap367:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap367:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap367:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap367:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma ankolapupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap367:6.1":"Ankolapupphiyattherassapadanam pancamam. "}